{"equipmentId": 422, "equipmentName": "FR-1 Fireball", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/FR-1%20Fireball", "pageEquipmentId": 422, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": false, "currentMethodTypes": ["event", "exchange", "quest", "ranking"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務『改装特務空母「Gambier Bay Mk.II」抜描！』選択報酬", "links": [{"text": "改装特務空母「Gambier Bay Mk.II」抜描！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B170"}, {"text": "震電改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9C%87%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "零式艦戦53型(岩本隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A653%E5%9E%8B%28%E5%B2%A9%E6%9C%AC%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "烈風 一一型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務『改装特務空母「Gambier Bay Mk.II」抜描！』選択報酬", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "ちなみに選択の対抗は戦果+800と現状唯一の単発任務系の戦果砲になる。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "ちなみに選択の対抗は戦果+800と現状唯一の単発任務系の戦果砲になる。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "(通称火の玉砲)", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "(通称火の玉砲)", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "80%で故意に残す提督はほぼほぼ戦果800砲として然るべき時に備えて持っている提督だろうが、結局読み合いである。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "使うならやはり連合ランカー狙う時だろうか。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "無論塩漬けしている提督もいるだろうが", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "ただし使ったからといって特に連合や1群に入れるかはその時の競争人数に左右される。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "本装備を放棄して戦果を獲得したが希望のランカーになれなかったら大損なのでそこだけは注意。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "ちなみに戦果+800はガチランカーが1日中稼いで獲得できる戦果程度にはなるが…", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["event"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "震電改等最上位艦戦が（期間限定等とはいえ)複数実装された2025年の現在、本装備はどちらかといえばイベント時(ほぼ欧州もとい夏イベ)の特効艦載機という枠になりつつあり、提督によっては通常使用しない提督もいるだろう。その点も選択の検討の一つになるだろう。", "links": [{"text": "震電改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9C%87%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}], "methodCount": 10, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 3, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvidence": {"cacheKey": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/FR-1%20Fireball.html", "rawPath": "data/raw_data/site_cache/wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/FR-1%20Fireball.html", "contentSha256": "5102e7221a6a7834ade6d9c2906a00f0c9f19fa023ce25a91c79b2b56dccd0ec", "fetchedAt": 1783246156, "validatedAt": 1783246156, "acquisitionSource": "external-browser-session-crawl"}, "fetchAttempts": [{"candidateSource": "raw-cache", "status": "ok", "url": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/FR-1%20Fireball", "cachePath": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/FR-1%20Fireball.html", "contentSha256": "5102e7221a6a7834ade6d9c2906a00f0c9f19fa023ce25a91c79b2b56dccd0ec"}]}
