{"equipmentId": 474, "equipmentName": "F4U-4", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4U-4", "pageEquipmentId": 474, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": false, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "event", "improvement", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["event", "exchange"], "methods": [{"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "F4U-2 Night Corsairからの改修更新。", "links": [{"text": "F4U-2 Night Corsair", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4U-2%20Night%20Corsair"}, {"text": "SB2C-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/SB2C-3"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "F4U-2 Night Corsair★max自体が非常に優秀な夜戦であるため、更新するかどうかはよく考えた方がよい。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "2025年6月現在通常海域で入手可能なGambier Bayが持ってくるFM-2から各種資材の消費を度外視すれば量産可能。", "links": [{"text": "Gambier Bay", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Gambier%20Bay"}, {"text": "FM-2", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/FM-2"}, {"text": "Intrepid改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Intrepid%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "F4U-1D", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4U-1D"}, {"text": "F6F-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F6F-3"}, {"text": "零式艦戦21型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "零式艦戦52型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A652%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "紫電改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B4%AB%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "試製烈風 後期型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "F4F-4", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4F-4"}, {"text": "SB2C-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/SB2C-3"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"