 "current", "rawText": "開発資材380個と改修資材223個(★+6以降を確実化する場合)、新型航空兵装資材x6、熟練搭乗員x1、海外艦最新技術x8", "links": [{"text": "FM-2", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/FM-2"}, {"text": "零式艦戦21型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "零式艦戦52型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A652%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "紫電改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B4%AB%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "試製烈風 後期型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "F4F-4", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4F-4"}, {"text": "F6F-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F6F-3"}, {"text": "SB2C-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/SB2C-3"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "零式艦戦21型x6、零式艦戦52型x18、紫電改二x12、試製烈風 後期型x8、F4F-4x1、F6F-3x1、SB2C-3×1。", "links": [{"text": "FM-2", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/FM-2"}, {"text": "零式艦戦21型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "零式艦戦52型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A652%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "紫電改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B4%AB%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "試製烈風 後期型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "F4F-4", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4F-4"}, {"text": "F6F-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F6F-3"}, {"text": "SB2C-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/SB2C-3"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "F4U-1Dから改修更新で本装備を作るには下記の資材・装備が必要となる。", "links": [{"text": "F4U-1D", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4U-1D"}, {"text": "零式艦戦52型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%