{"equipmentId": 490, "equipmentName": "試製 夜間瑞雲(攻撃装備)", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD%20%E5%A4%9C%E9%96%93%E7%91%9E%E9%9B%B2%28%E6%94%BB%E6%92%83%E8%A3%85%E5%82%99%29", "pageEquipmentId": 490, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": false, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "exchange", "improvement", "quest", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["development", "quest", "ranking"], "methods": [{"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "「瑞雲改二(六三四空)★max」からの改修更新 。", "links": [{"text": "瑞雲改二(六三四空)★max", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%9B%B2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C%28%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%9B%E7%A9%BA%29"}, {"text": "改修更新", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%A8#id322"}, {"text": "量産も夢ではない…", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/p/cushion?to=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKanColle_STAFF%2Fstatus%2F1625501523018121218"}, {"text": "瑞雲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%9B%B2"}, {"text": "瑞雲12型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%9B%B212%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "瑞雲(六三四空)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%9B%B2%28%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%9B%E7%A9%BA%29"}, {"text": "瑞雲改二(六三四空)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%9B%B2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C%28%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%9B%E7%A9%BA%29"}, {"text": "九七式艦攻改 試製三号戊型(空六号電探改装備機)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%94%BB%E6%94%B9%20%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%B7%E6%88%8A%E5%9E%8B%28%E7%A9%BA%E5%85%AD%E5%8F%B7%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2%E6%94%B9%E8%A3%85%E5%82%99%E6%A9%9F%29"}, {"text": "雲鷹改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B2%E9%B7%B9%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "八幡丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%85%AB%E5%B9%A1%E4%B8%B8"}, {"text": "海上護衛！ヒ船団を護り抜け！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B176"}, {"text": "航空母艦「雲鷹」、抜錨せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B177"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "実際に瑞雲から作成した場合、まず改修資材が800以上吹っ飛ぶ。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "熟練搭乗員もかなりの数を消費するのも厳しいところ。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発資材も改修分だけで1300以上、消費装備分の瑞雲等も開発で調達するとなると、もはや開発資材は3000で足りるかどうかというレベル。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "……といった具合なので、作成する場合はなるべく上位の瑞雲機体を素体にスタートして消費資材を節約しよう。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "瑞雲改二(六三四空)からの更新には九七式艦攻改 試製三号戊型(空六号電探改装備機)を使用するのもボトルネックの一つ。", "links": [{"text": "瑞雲改二(六三四空)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%9B%B2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C%28%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%9B%E7%A9%BA%29"}, {"text": "九七式艦攻改 試製三号戊型(空六号電探改装備機)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%94%BB%E6%94%B9%20%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%B7%E6%88%8A%E5%9E%8B%28%E7%A9%BA%E5%85%AD%E5%8F%B7%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2%E6%94%B9%E8%A3%85%E5%82%99%E6%A9%9F%29"}, {"text": "雲鷹改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B2%E9%B7%B9%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "八幡丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%85%AB%E5%B9%A1%E4%B8%B8"}, {"text": "海上護衛！ヒ船団を護り抜け！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B176"}, {"text": "航空母艦「雲鷹」、抜錨せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B177"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "雲鷹改", "shipId": 382, "shipName": "雲鷹改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "linkTarget": "雲鷹改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B2%E9%B7%B9%E6%94%B9"}, {"rawName": 