["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "秋月型を秘書艦にする事で、ペンギン率が更に2%高くなるので、できれば彼女らに任せたい。", "links": [{"text": "秋月型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%89%A6%E5%A8%98%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%EF%BC%88%E8%89%A6%E7%A8%AE%E5%88%A5%EF%BC%89#Class_Akizuki"}, {"text": "天津風", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A9%E6%B4%A5%E9%A2%A8"}, {"text": "深雪改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B7%B1%E9%9B%AA%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "吹雪型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%89%A6%E5%A8%98%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%EF%BC%88%E8%89%A6%E7%A8%AE%E5%88%A5%EF%BC%89#Class_Fubuki"}, {"text": "25mm単装機銃", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/25mm%E5%8D%98%E8%A3%85%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%83"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "高射装置が開発可能になり失敗率が下がった。", "links": [{"text": "秋月型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%89%A6%E5%A8%98%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%EF%BC%88%E8%89%A6%E7%A8%AE%E5%88%A5%EF%BC%89#Class_Akizuki"}, {"text": "天津風", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A9%E6%B4%A5%E9%A2%A8"}, {"text": "深雪改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B7%B1%E9%9B%AA%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "吹雪型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%89%A6%E5%A8%98%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%EF%BC%88%E8%89%A6%E7%A8%AE%E5%88%A5%EF%BC%89#Class_Fubuki"}, {"text": "25mm単装機銃", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/25mm%E5%8D%98%E8%A3%85%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%83"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "天津風が鋼材テーブルでもボーキテーブルでも失敗率が変わらないため効率がいい。", "links": [{"text": "秋月型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%89%A6%E5%A8%98%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%EF%BC%88%E8%89%A6%E7%A8%AE%E5%88%A5%EF%BC%89#Class_Akizuki"}, {"text": "天津風", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A9%E6%B4%A5%E9%A2%A8"}, {"text": "深雪改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B7%B1%E9%9B%AA%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "吹雪型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%