{"equipmentId": 520, "equipmentName": "試製20.3cm(4号)連装砲", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD20.3cm%284%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2", "pageEquipmentId": 520, "sectionHeading": "入手方法", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": false, "currentMethodTypes": ["exchange", "improvement", "quest", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["event", "exchange", "quest"], "methods": [{"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "20.3cm(3号)連装砲からの改修更新。", "links": [{"text": "20.3cm(3号)連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%283%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}, {"text": "20.3cm連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "後半に共食いして改修の難易度が爆上がりする同装備からの更新ということで、要求される装備はどうなるか戦々恐々した提督も多かっただろう。", "links": [{"text": "20.3cm連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "…が、同装備を★maxにした提督へのご褒美なのか、なんと本装備への更新から★maxまですべて20.3cm連装砲で賄える手軽さを誇る。", "links": [{"text": "20.3cm連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "むしろ更新時に必要な新型砲熕兵装資材2個、新型兵装資材1個のせいで量産できない可能性の方が高い", "links": [{"text": "20.3cm連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "その代わり、必要な数が非常に多いが*7、20.3cm連装砲は持参する重巡が非常に多いため、コツコツ改修する分には困ることはないだろう。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務『改装航空巡洋艦「三隈」、進発せよ！』選択報酬（★+2）*8", "links": [{"text": "改装航空巡洋艦「三隈」、進発せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B196"}, {"text": "秋刀魚祭り【拡張任務二〇二四】フィナーレ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2024-9"}, {"text": "【艦隊12周年記念任務:拡張任務】特別工廠", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2025-7"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務『改装航空巡洋艦「三隈」、進発せよ！』選択報酬（★+2）*8", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "event"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2024年 鎮守府秋刀魚祭り『秋刀魚祭り【拡張任務二〇二四】フィナーレ！』確定報酬 (★+2)", "links": [{"text": "秋刀魚祭り【拡張任務二〇二四】フィナーレ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2024-9"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "2024年 鎮守府秋刀魚祭り『秋刀魚祭り【拡張任務二〇二四】フィナーレ！』確定報酬 (★+2)", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2025年 艦隊12周年記念『【艦隊12周年記念任務:拡張任務】特別工廠』選択報酬", "links": [{"text": "【艦隊12周年記念任務:拡張任務】特別工廠", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2025-7"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "2025年 艦隊12周年記念『【艦隊12周年記念任務:拡張任務】特別工廠』選択報酬", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}], "methodCount": 8, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 3, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvide